                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">可以用来开拓新闻史研究的视野。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="675823954">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-675823954" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-675823954" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="675823954">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jinfeixing/">孔劼</a>
